file.string: Adjust scale of the map display
Select language of multilingual map (multilingual map must be loaded)
Show both local and preferred language
Set units system on the scale bar
Debugging aid for setting maximum textwidth
Way filtering reduces the number of ways returned at the risk of clipping artifacts
The higher the number the less artifacts, but slower
Number of threads to render concurrently
To run this samples app, you need any map with filename berlin.map installed on storage.\n\nadb push file.map /sdcard/Android/data/org.mapsforge.samples.android/files/berlin.map
To run this sample activity, you need a TMS tile store at /sdcard/Android/data/org.mapsforge.samples.android/files/tilestore. Sample data in the app data directory.
To run this sample activity, you need to download a low-resolution world map first.
To run this sample activity, you need also a map with filename second.map installed on storage.
To run this sample activity, you need any poi with filename berlin.poi installed on storage.\n\nadb push file.poi /sdcard/Android/data/org.mapsforge.samples.android/files/berlin.poi
